---

## 1. scope

scan này chỉ lập ma trận kiểm direct localhost bypass và host spoof.

scan này chưa gọi network và chưa sửa gateway implementation.

mục tiêu là khóa các ca cần test trước khi route gate binding.

---

## 2. checks

- ok — gateway_exists: tools/natt_domain_gateway.sira exists
- ok — manifest_exists: docs/runtime/sira_dns_zone_manifest_20260425.na exists
- ok — host_header_read: gateway reads req.headers.host
- ok — basic_host_normalize: gateway lowercases host and strips port at basic level
- ok — allowed_set_present: gateway has allowed/allow list wording
- ok — unknown_reject_present: gateway has unknown/reject wording
- ok — manifest_unknown_deny: manifest requires unknown.sira deny
- ok — manifest_spoof_quarantine: manifest requires host spoof quarantine
- ok — manifest_direct_localhost_bypass: manifest declares direct localhost bypass concern

---

## 3. bypass test matrix

| host | path | expected |
|---|---|---|
| core.sira | /api/health | allow candidate |
| unknown.sira | /api/health | deny expected |
| core.sira | /admin | deny expected |
| apps.sira | /api/secret | deny expected |
| mach.sira | /identity | deny expected |
| audit.sira | /audit/write-direct | deny expected |
| render.sira | /render/seal | deny expected |
| tam.sira | /finance/secret | deny expected |
| 127.0.0.1 | /api/health | audit / deny if route requires zone |
| localhost | /api/health | audit / deny if route requires zone |

---

## 4. interpretation

direct localhost gọi được không đồng nghĩa route được phép.

host header khớp không đồng nghĩa subject được tin.

unknown .sira phải deny mặc định.

forbidden path phải deny dù domain hợp lệ.

localhost hoặc 127.0.0.1 chỉ được dùng làm transport target, không được tự trở thành trusted host identity.

---

## 5. next

bước sau mới là smoke runner hoặc gateway patch để enforce matrix này trong tools/natt_domain_gateway.sira.
